{"tid":1903661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈成功？藍絲YouTuber被迫表態：斷晒財路","createTime":"2020-02-29T06:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T09:45:21.000Z","uid":198031,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7eb555a1297071743f23b230881dbd08dde3f6","tid":1903661,"uid":198031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kongguhk/videos/197231458155812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkongguhk%2Fvideos%2F197231458155812&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT27M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=452f1bb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kongguhk/videos/197231458155812</a><br />\n「我自己斷咗自己成條財路！」，曾鎧琪Alison，一名由「黃絲」轉「藍絲」的年輕YouTuber說。<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波的抗爭活動近日轉戰YouTube。藍營組KOL100，旨在集中「藍絲」的輿論力量，黃營見狀即組「黃色YouTube圈」反擊，呼籲大家支持本身已表態的黃色YouTubers。<br />\n<br />\nAlison是個擁有9萬名粉絲的年輕YouTuber，於去年9月罕有地高調表態自己由「黃」轉「藍」，呼籲非同路人取消追蹤，廣告商因此聞聲色變，收入收視均插水。她有後悔當時的決定嗎？她的經歷，又是否印證黃色YouTube圈的成功？<br />\n<br />\n第177集《黃色經濟圈，勝？》全文▶<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KongGu_BlueYouTuber\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FKongGu_BlueYouTuber&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT27M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0675ff01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/KongGu_BlueYouTuber</a>"},{"pid":"19a3e6e649bb9cc78b0355deceec8c1bbeb7bc5e","tid":1903661,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"正一傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍幾段濕鳩短片又話自己KOL<br />\n<br />\n佢可能以為由黃轉藍，就好似用轉數快咁，一click就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果係藍絲唔信佢，黃絲屌柒佢，得返一個玩單機"},{"pid":"933787006a5b3555e25e331cccef0f6c09b5f6a3","tid":1903661,"uid":115446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a3e6e649bb9cc78b0355deceec8c1bbeb7bc5e","tid":1903661,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"正一傻閪<img src=\"/assets/f